        public double[] generate(double[][] A,
                         double[] b,
                         GLPSolver solver)
                  throws UnboundedSystemException,
                         InfeasibleSystemException
        Finds an interior point of Ax ≤ b by maximization of a slack variable. Note that the system is required to be bounded and full-dimensional.
        Parameters:
        A - matrix A
        b - vector b
        solver - solver
        Returns:
        interior point
        Throws:
        UnboundedSystemException - if unbounded
        InfeasibleSystemException - if not feasible
